msgid "Details to include in a User Forum post"
msgstr "Manylion i'w gynnwys ym mhost Fforwm Defnyddwyr"

#: templates/pages/community/support.html:85
msgid ""
"\n"
"                <p>Depending on the nature of your issue, here's a few ideas of the information that will help us respond to you more quickly and in more precise detail:</p>\n"
"                <ul>\n"
"                  <li>What version of AtoM are you using?</li>\n"
"                  <li>What have you tried already to resolve the problem?</li>\n"
"                  <li>What operating system is AtoM installed on (Linux, Windows, Apple, etc.)?\n"
"                  <li>What version of PHP do you have installed?</li>\n"
"                  <li>Do you have a stack trace of the error message you received?</li>\n"
"                  <li>Are you hosting your own instance, or are you using an external hosting provider?</li>\n"
"                </ul>\n"
"                <p>We find it easiest to clearly answer posts that are <strong>complete</strong> and <strong>succinct</strong> - that is, posts that include all important details about the software environment and what led to the error, but that also trim away any details  or code snippets that aren't directly relevant to the mater at hand. Thanks for helping us to make the User Forum a vibrant and positive place!</p>\n"
"              "
msgstr "\n                <p>Yn dibynnu ar natur y mater, dyma rai syniadau o'r wybodaeth a fydd yn ein helpu i ymateb yn gyflymach ac yn fwy manwl:</p>\n                <ul>\n                  <li>Pa fersiwn o AtoM ydych chi'n ei defnyddio?</li>\n                  <li>Beth ydych chi wedi ei wneud eisoes i geisio datrys y broblem?</li>\n                  <li>Ar ba system weithredu y mae AtoM wedi ei osod (Linux, Windows, Apple, ayyb.)?\n                  <li>Pa fersiwn o PHP sydd wedi ei osod?</li>\n                  <li>A oes gennych stac olrhain o'r neges wall a gawsoch?</li>\n                  <li>A ydych yn cynnal eich achos eich hun, neu a ydych yn defnyddio gwesteiwr allanol?</li>\n                </ul>\n                <p>Rydym yn ei chael yn haws i ateb yn glir postiadau sydd yn <strong>gyflawn</strong> a <strong>chryno</strong> - hynny yw, postiadau sy'n cynnwys yr holl fanylion pwysig am amgylchedd y meddalwedd a beth arweiniodd at y gwall, ond bod hefyd eithrio unrhyw fanylion neu bytiau cod nad ydynt yn uniongyrchol berthnasol i'r mater dan sylw. Diolch am ein helpu i wneud y Fforwm Defnyddwyr yn lle bywiog a chadarnhaol!</p>\n              "

